Ensure the TESTNG tests are grouped in the following way::
Hint: https://maven.apache.org/surefire/maven-surefire-plugin/examples/testng.html

groups={"regression","sendmessages","ui"}

groups={"sanity","sendmessages","ui"}

groups={"sanity","sendmessages","api"}

Run all sendMessagestests => 3 
Run all sanity => 2
Run all sendmessages ,regression,ui -> 1

*****Run all  regression,ui -> 1


pom.xml 
	group name= ui,regression
